<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٦٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالصَّابِؤُونَ}</span> ... قَوْمٌ بَاقُونَ عَلَى فِطْرَتِهِمْ، وَلَا دِينَ لَهُمْ يَتَّبِعُونَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٧١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِتْنَةٌ}</span> ... عَذَابٌ، وَبَلَاءٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٧٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صِدِّيقَةٌ}</span> ... قَدْ صَدَّقَتْ تَصْدِيقًا جَازِمًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٧٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا تَغْلُوا}</span> ... لَا تَتَجَاوَزُوا الحَقَّ فِي اعْتِقَادِكُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قِسِّيسِينَ}</span> ... عُلَمَاءَ النَّصَارَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٨٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرُهْبَانًا}</span> ... عُبَّادَ النَّصَارَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَفِيضُ}</span> ... تَمْتَلِئُ دَمْعًا، فَيَنْسَكِبُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الشَّاهِدِينَ}</span> ... الَّذِينَ يَشْهَدُونَ عَلَى الأَمَمِ السَّابِقِةَ، وَهُمْ أُمَّةُ نَبِيِّنَا مُحَمَّدٍ - صلى الله عليه وسلم -.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَثَابَهُمُ}</span> ... جَزَاهُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِاللَّغْوِ}</span> ... مَا لَا يَقْصِدُهُ الْحَالِفُ؛<span class="c5"> كَقَوْلِهِ:</span> لَا وَاللهِ، وَبَلَى وَاللهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَقَّدتُّمُ}</span> ... قَصَدتُّمْ عَقْدَهُ بِقُلُوبِكُمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٨٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَاحْفَظُوا أَيْمَانَكُمْ}</span> ... اجْتَنِبُوا اليَمِينَ مِنْ غَيْرِ حَاجَةٍ، وَإِنْ أَوْقَعْتُمُوهَا فَوَفُّوا بِهَا، وَكَفِّرُوهَا إِن لَّمْ تَفُوا بِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٩٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْمَيْسِرُ}</span> ... القِمَارُ، وَهُوَ المُرَاهَنَاتُ الَّتِي فِيهَا عِوَضٌ مِنَ الجَانِبَيْنِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>